 - Show Preview window when join a conference from link, Press continue if microphone works
 - Bring window in front when incomming call arrives
 - Audio indication when the conference start (2nd party joins the conference the first time)
 - Auto login on start or after failure to register
 - Auto answer for given addresses after predefined delay and chosen media type
 - Call history menu
 - Most called numbers on main screen for easy visual redial (like big tiles)
 - Address book lookup for Mac
 - Output/Alert device selection
 - Text chat sessions
 - File transfer support (drag and drop for desktop)
 - Screen sharing support (and/or second camera feed)
 - Local video recording
 - Edit display name after join a conference without account 
 - Streaming to external video broadcast service
